comment: First differs from A305193 at a(36) = 4, A305193(36) = 5.
a(n) depends only on prime signature of n (cf. A025487). - _Antti Karttunen_, Nov 07 2018

program: (PARI) A319786(n, m=n, facs=List([])) = if(1==n, (1!=gcd(Vec(facs))), my(s=0, newfacs); fordiv(n, d, if((d>1)&&(d<=m), newfacs = List(facs); listput(newfacs,d); s += A319786(n/d, d, newfacs))); (s)); \\ _Antti Karttunen_, Nov 07 2018
